reviews.review_text: better than Cornell i dont see how this isnt the best dead show...EVER
great show but Vince Welnicks backing vocals on "Mighty Swell" make Phil Lesh's "I knoooow U Ride-AHH" 1974 backing vocals sound like Pavarotti

MEET UP AT THE MOVIES I just watched this show at the 2019 Meetup at the Movies. Unfortunately, Playing in the Band was slightly accelerated. I wonder if this was a mixing error or was it an impatient projectionist trying to get this show over with?

The show is amazing.

Would have been even better if it was in our local historic theater. How hard would it be for the Dead office to work through independent theaters instead of corporate? Maybe too complicated but it would enhance the experience.
